snippet.title: Papetura: Gameplay Short Trailer
snippet.description:
Papetura is an atmospheric adventure game handcrafted entirely from paper. Little creatures Pape and Tura will face monsters that will try to burn down their beloved world.
Out on Steam! http://steam.pm/app/593640​ ang Gog! http://gog.com/game/papetura​

Music by
Floex - Tomas Dvorak - http://floex.cz​

Sfx by
Juraj Mravec - http://www.jurajmravec.co.uk/​

Visit Papetura homepage to see more:
http://papetura.com/​

Papetura on Social Media:
https://twitter.com/PapeturaGame​
https://www.facebook.com/papetura/​
